🧩 Word Scramble Game

A simple JavaScript console game where the player has to guess the correct word from a scrambled version.

🚀 Features

Randomly picks a word from a list.

Scrambles the letters of the word.

Lets the player keep guessing until they get it right.

Gives instant feedback: ✅ Correct / ❌ Wrong.

📋 Requirements

Node.js installed on your system.

readline-sync package for user input.

🔧 Installation & Setup

Clone or download the file.

Open a terminal in the project folder.

Install the dependency:

npm install readline-sync


Run the game:

node index.js

🎮 How to Play

The program will show you a scrambled word.

Type your guess in the console.

If correct → 🎉 you win!

If wrong → ❌ try again until you succeed.

📂 Example Run
Unscramble this word: aepch = peach
🎉 Correct! The word is peach

📝 Customization

You can add more words in the words array:

let words = ["apple", "banana", "grapes", "orange", "peach", "mango", "cherry"];